  "text": "Here n r , n c are the dimensions of the output and input of the LTI system H respectively. The solution to problem (9) is independent of t as long as t > r + i + \u03c4 . Following the proofs of Theorem 6.1 and 6.2 in [CITATION_1] , we can show that\u03bd",
